      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The tunnel was one of the chief\npower developments figured on by\nthe Washington Water Power COM\npany two years ago when it author\nlied the issuance of $15.0OO,000 in\nbonds for gigantic extensions of\nvarious kinds.\n\n\nSince then the Post Falls dam\nhas been completed, the dam at\nLittle Falls nearly SO, immense\nbuildings have been erected and the\ntracks of the company's street rail-\nway system in Spokane practically\nrebuilt and scores Of new cars put\non the city lines.\n\n\nThe last and greatest Of all IL\nthe immense tunnel proposition on\nwhich work was begun this week."
